<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>١١٩٠ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَلِأَبِي الْعَتَاهِيَةِ:</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
